At least 500 acres of vegetation at the Kenya Agricultural and Livestock Research Organisation (Kalro) in Lanet were destroyed by fire at the weekend. Kalro Director Naftali Ondabu said the fire broke out at around 4pm on Saturday. ALSO READ:

